The subscription terms of use can be found here. (https://www.walmart.com/help/article/walmart-subscriptions-terms-of-use/f05e20e6c2544640a88cfa2aa4947aac)

Subscriptions are available on thousands of everyday favorites such as groceries, pet supplies, pantry staples, home cleaning and more. If the item is eligible, you will be able to select “Subscribe” & choose how often you want your item. To participate, you must have a valid Walmart account, shipping address & payment method on file. Sign into your account or create a new account to get started.

There is no charge to subscribe to items. Shipping is free on orders over $35. Certain items eligible for subscriptions may require a scheduled delivery. Delivery fees apply to all scheduled deliveries.  A minimum order fee of $6.99 applies to all orders below $35, and bag fees may apply to delivery orders in certain locations.

Walmart+ members can start using subscriptions at no added cost to membership and get free shipping and delivery on all orders. Any delivery order under $35 will still be subject to the minimum order fee.

You can easily manage your subscriptions in the app or online. Log in to your account & select My Subscriptions under Subscription & Plans section. Select the subscription you wish to skip. Select “Skip” on each item you would like to skip.
You can easily manage your subscriptions in the app or online. Log in to your account, click account & select My Subscriptions. Click on the subscription you wish to cancel. Select “Unsubscribe”.

You can easily manage your subscriptions in the app or online. Log in to your account and select My Subscriptions. Click on the subscription you wish to change. Select “Edit” next to frequency. Update the frequency to your requested change.

You can easily manage your subscriptions in the app or online. Log in to your account & select My Subscriptions. Select “Edit” on the right of the screen. Choose your new delivery day and/or time.
We aim to deliver low prices and don’t expect them to change often. We’ll let you know the price you’ll be charged prior to each fulfillment.
No, not all items are available for subscription service. Please see the individual item page for details.
Subscription orders follow normal return processes.

While your order is still preparing, you can add or remove items, increase or decrease quantities, and allow or disallow substitutions. To edit items in an order, select Account, select Purchase History, and select Edit Items.
